    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "ファン！　感！　謝！　祭！　ですよー！",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんだ、急に\nテンションが高くないか？",
      "startTime": 6.6235907674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです！\n最高の気分ですよ！　うふふ、うふふふ！",
      "startTime": 10.2333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "だって、だって……憧れの曲！　『GIRI-GIRI\nborderless world』を――",
      "startTime": 18.6666677475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "四人で歌えることになったんですから！",
      "startTime": 20.718572267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワのファン感謝祭でやるリメイク曲……\n二人時代の曲を四人で歌う企画だな",
      "startTime": 27.9000010808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ファン投票でこの曲に決まったじゃないですか！\n私もすっごくすっごく好きな曲なので、嬉しいんです！",
      "startTime": 35.3666677475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……莉央さんと葵さんのクールなのに熱い歌声に\n練習生時代から、何度励まされてきたことか……",
      "startTime": 45.4000026067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "それを、私達も同じステージで一緒に歌えるなんて\n夢みたいです……！",
      "startTime": 53.4333359401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、私達の衣装も作ってもらえるそうですし！",
      "startTime": 55.149162992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "GIRI-GIRIまで全力で\n命の音を燃やしてみせます！",
      "startTime": 61.3000013352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "歌詞を引用するほど好きなんだな……",
      "startTime": 63.7420866332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃもう！　何度も生で観てますけど\nパフォーマンスはもちろん、衣装もかっこ良くて",
      "startTime": 69.9666680019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "何から何まで最高で……\nくぅ～！　思い出すだけで震えちゃいます！",
      "startTime": 76.6333346685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "そんな憧れの曲に参加出来るんだーって思うと\n身体の芯から、エネルギーがカッとわき上がってきて",
      "startTime": 84.4111592509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "どうにもじっとしてられないんです！",
      "startTime": 88.6454406582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、愛にとって大事な曲なんだな\nでも、あまり飛ばし過ぎないようにしてくれよ",
      "startTime": 95.5666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です！\nあの憧れの衣装を着るまでは倒れません！",
      "startTime": 99.8999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、衣装を着てからが本番なんだが\nそこで倒れないように頼む……",
      "startTime": 106.3999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "はっ、そうでした……！\n本当の意味で夢になっちゃうところでした",
      "startTime": 110.7999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "早速今からレッスンなので、行ってきますね！\n前を向き駆け抜けろですよ！",
      "startTime": 118.1333290736,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8633.337593100008,
          "startTime": 126.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ見せつけますよ、負けないって！\nなんせチカラがわき上がってきてますからねー！",
      "startTime": 123.5666598637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、頑張れよ……って、もういない\n随分張り切ってるなぁ",
      "startTime": 132.3844316434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 135.8203122618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "空見上げた……あの頃から……踊りながら……",
      "startTime": 139.2666624069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　どうしたんだ、愛。休憩中か？",
      "startTime": 146.1294061504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "命の音燃ーっやーっしーって！",
      "startTime": 149.5208800319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ！？",
      "startTime": 152.5516271754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "あれっ？　あ、{user}さん\nお疲れ様です！",
      "startTime": 155.3029134608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "おいおい\nここはレッスンルームじゃないんだぞ",
      "startTime": 158.8666593551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません！",
      "startTime": 161.4087907198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai022.m4a",
      "text": "以前のMVを観ながらパートの確認をしてたんですけど\n聴いてたら、つい、盛り上がっちゃって……",
      "startTime": 167.7666603724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、そのひたむきに努力する姿勢は\n愛のいいところだと思うけどな",
      "startTime": 173.763233982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai023.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 176.296247749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さらに数日後",
      "startTime": 180.6873412574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
